Loss(cost) function
usual function - regression : MSE=(1/n)*Sigma(y-y')^2
               - classifier : - LogisiticRegression -> Logistic loss function : -(y*log(a)+(1-y)*log(1-a))
                              - crossentropy : - binary
                                               - categorial
                                               
Logistic loss function : when y=1(양의 클래스) a have to be 1 for classify correctly
                         when y=0(음의 클래스) a have to be 0 for classify correctly
